OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fgrandmother faces Christmas
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FDay on her own             
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A grandmother was looking forward to   
OL,6, cooking Christmas dinner for her three 
OL,7, children and five grandchildren - but  
OL,8, will now be spending the day alone.    
OL,10,FMandy Connors, from Aberystwyth, tested
OL,11,Fpositive for Covid on Tuesday and will 
OL,12,Fnow join the festivities via FaceTime. 
OL,14,FRules state that if you have tested    
OL,15,Fpositive for Covid-19, you must        
OL,16,Fself-isolate for 10 days.              
OL,18,FThere are potentially tens of thousands
OL,19,Fof people in Wales, positive since 16  
OL,20,FDecember, who will spend the day alone.
